Package: clumpedr
Title: Clumped isotope analysis in R
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: person("Ilja", "Kocken", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2196-8718"), email = "iljakocken at gmail.com")
URL: https://github.com/isoverse/clumpedr
BugReports: https://github.com/isoverse/clumpedr/issues
Description: Data processing in clumped isotopes is an involved, evolving field. This package aims facilitate the processing of raw data to final \eqn{\Delta_{47}}{Î”47} values and temperatures, step-by-step, with good documentation, so that the full process is easier to understand and tweak, more reproducible, and fully transparent.
